{"word":"Bethlehem","slug":"bethlehem","sections":[{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":""},{"paragraph":"<b>Bethlehem</b> 1. A city southwest of Jerusalem<br/> - General references<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=17&verse=7'>Jdg 17:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=19&verse=18'>Jdg 19:18</a> <br/> - Called Ephratah<br/> - Called Ephrath<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=48&verse=7'>Gen 48:7</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=19&chapter=132&verse=6'>Psa 132:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=5&verse=2'>Mic 5:2</a> <br/> - Called Bethlehem-Judah<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=17&verse=9'>Jdg 17:9</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=19&verse=1'>Jdg 19:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=19&verse=18'>Jdg 19:18</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=1&verse=1'>Rth 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=9&chapter=17&verse=12'>1Sa 17:12</a> <br/> - Rachel dies and is buried at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=16'>Gen 35:16</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=35&verse=19'>Gen 35:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=1&chapter=48&verse=7'>Gen 48:7</a> <br/> - The city of Boaz<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=1&verse=1'>Rth 1:1</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=1&verse=19'>Rth 1:19</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=2&verse=4'>Rth 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=8&chapter=4'>Rth 4</a> <br/> - Taken and held by the Philistines<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=10&chapter=23&verse=16'>2Sa 23:16</a> <br/> - Jeroboam converts it into a military stronghold<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=14&chapter=11&verse=6'>2Ch 11:6</a> <br/> - The city of Joseph<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=6'>Mat 2:6</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=4'>Luk 2:4</a> <br/> - Birthplace of Jesus<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=33&chapter=5&verse=2'>Mic 5:2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2'>Mat 2</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=4'>Luk 2:4</a>; <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=42&chapter=2&verse=15'>Luk 2:15</a> <br/> - Herod slays the children of<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=40&chapter=2&verse=18'>Mat 2:18</a> <br/> 2. A town of Zebulun<br/> - Six miles west of Nazareth<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=6&chapter=19&verse=15'>Jos 19:15</a> <br/> - Israel judged at<br/> <a href='https://www.wordofgod.in/bibles/?book=7&chapter=12&verse=10'>Jdg 12:10</a> "}]}